Package: ddc-cwicr-cli
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), ddc-qdrant
Recommends: ddc-cwicr-en | ddc-cwicr-de | ddc-cwicr-ru | ddc-cwicr-fr | ddc-cwicr-es | ddc-cwicr-ar | ddc-cwicr-zh | ddc-cwicr-pt | ddc-cwicr-hi
Maintainer: DataDrivenConstruction.io
Homepage: https://github.com/datadrivenconstruction/OpenConstructionEstimate-DDC-CWICR
Description: CLI search tool for DDC CWICR construction cost database
 Command-line interface for searching construction work items,
 materials, labor rates, and equipment costs.
 .
 Supports semantic search (via OpenAI embeddings) and keyword search.
 Auto-detects installed language collections.
 .
 Usage: ddc-search "reinforced concrete foundation"
        ddc-search --keyword "concrete"
        ddc-search --list
Installed-Size: 24
